UNITED STATES ex rel. Keith M. BALL, etc., Relator-Appellee, v. Benjamin M. DAY, as Commissioner, etc., Respondent-Appellant. No. 266. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 3, 1930. Leon B. Spencer, of New York City, for appellant. John E. Stevens, of New York City, for appellee.

Before L. HAND, AUGUSTUS N. HAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed in open court.
